;*****************************************************************************
;
; Name:  zebrmsw.inf
;
; Function:
;	Install Sony Ericsson WDM drivers
;
; Copyright (c) 2006 Moore Computer Consultants, Inc.
;
; MCCI is a registered trademark of Moore Computer Consultants, Inc.
;
